Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.31,0:00:18.41,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0015,,{\blur3}I have a big gun, I took it from my Lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.55,0:00:21.79,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Sick with Justice, I just wanna feel you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.02,0:00:25.20,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm your angel, only a ring away...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.32,0:00:28.55,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You make me violate you, no matter who you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.53,0:00:38.67,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It's all up to you, no one lives forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.87,0:00:42.26,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Been burn in the hell, by all those pigs out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.34,0:00:45.53,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It's always been hell, from when I was born...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.67,0:00:48.72,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}They make me violate them, no matter who they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.72,0:00:52.26,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs79}Get down on your knees! Get a good head on your shoulders!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.26,0:00:55.69,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}If it's for your guys, go to the end of the Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.69,0:00:59.00,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Do what you think, give it with dedication...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.00,0:01:02.27,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'll put out your misery!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.36,0:01:05.67,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You made a mess! For Christ sakes, this rotten world!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.67,0:01:09.10,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Shit out of luck! Go with my vision!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.10,0:01:12.54,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Light up the fire! Right on the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.54,0:01:15.90,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Weapon... I have it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.94,0:01:24.48,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Weapon... I have it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.92,0:01:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right? I told you so.\NLet's go again sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.43,0:01:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.30,0:01:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hey.\N- Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.78,0:02:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This probably isn't a very\Namusing place for a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.96,0:02:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No bother. But I do rather\Ndislike noisy places.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.13,0:02:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kousa clan is on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.30,0:02:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, in Roppongi, we don't\Nstand out like a sore thumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.03,0:02:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our neutralization of enemy targets\Nis proceeding according to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.04,0:02:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Kousa clan is\Na very large outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.64,0:02:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to go further to squeeze them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We move on to phase two\Nand institute a shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.91,0:02:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- A shift?\N- Yes, we shift gears.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.72,0:02:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First we clamp down on\Ntheir income sources...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.25,0:02:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...retailers, entertainment venues,\Nwaste management.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.02,0:02:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys aren't amateurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.82,0:02:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we keep this up, they're bound\Nto notice what we're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just to rattle their cage,\Nof course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our main target is something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.50,0:02:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.60,0:03:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will resort to a tactic\Nthat works in every nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.15,0:03:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Abduction. An abduction, Mr. Bando.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.62,0:03:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll target the family of the\NKousa clan head, Masami Kousa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.22,0:03:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.66,0:03:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to dampen the mood,\Nbut that's the one thing you can't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.70,0:03:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What was that?\N- He said, "We can't do that".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.23,0:03:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What we are looking for is a fight where\Nthe Kousa clan loosens their grip.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.10,0:03:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After you make a ruckus for a while,\Nwe can then lure them in with talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.04,0:03:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go overboard and make\Nthings difficult for us later on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.95,0:03:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear that, Sergeant?\NThey don't get it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.15,0:03:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, translate this carefully, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.69,0:03:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Bando.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.66,0:04:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will employ any means\Nnecessary to secure profits.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are taking on most of the risks here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.24,0:04:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, the decision-making\Nbelongs to us, not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.88,0:04:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you, Rumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.52,0:04:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to call me at\Nthis time of day. Huh? Prada?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.86,0:04:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want any. I've got enough\Nto sell. You talk too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch it or I'll take two of your teeth\Nout later. Huh? Then get false teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.93,0:04:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- I gotta go.\N- Chaka! What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.40,0:04:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you realize what we're\Ntalking about here, you idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry about that. That stupid bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.81,0:04:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Get outta here!\N- Yeah, sure. I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.64,0:04:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshida, let it go.\NI apologize for making a scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.28,0:04:50.37,Black Lagoon Book,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(717,608)\frz325.915}Martin Heidegger's\N"Holzwege"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.48,0:04:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yukio, you're still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.35,0:04:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Maki. Oh, my. Look at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you reading now, Yukio?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This? Martin Heidegger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's philosophical,\Nbut very powerful. I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.56,0:05:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass on it. I like skincare\Nguides and modern horror books.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did say you like Anne Rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.47,0:05:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you like for light reading, Yukio?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.14,0:05:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see. Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.41,0:05:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind. It's all right.\NForget that I asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you were just thinking about\Nprobably wasn't light reading at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so? I like any book that\Nmakes me feel like I'm out in the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.73,0:05:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Swallowing knowledge and\Nemotion and everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.10,0:05:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Endlessly expanding,\Nyet somewhat different from reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.44,0:05:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- I think that's what I like.\N- I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.77,0:05:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get into reading the\Ndifficult ones. How about King?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.18,0:05:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care for scary novels.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.21,0:05:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? That's a bit surprising.\NI would've thought you like Poe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like the ones that\Nmake you imagine the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So dark and lonely and sorrowful.\NI don't like the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.53,0:06:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get really scared, thinking\NI'll be sucked into this darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.30,0:06:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not romantic. Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.21,0:06:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- I hear we've got trouble.\N- They're waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Target 012 confirmed.\N- 012 confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't I have a little more time\Nbefore you go ahead with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'll wait, so long as it\Ndoes not interfere with the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.93,0:06:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that we can raise a toast\Nto each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.26,0:06:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mr. Taka. What's with that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! Haven't you\Nlearned your lesson yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.17,0:06:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.51,0:07:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's that skinny interpreter's\Nbody guard. From Roanapur.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.28,0:07:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? She's a woman and\Nshe can fight?! Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.45,0:07:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaka, you idiot!\NCut it out! They're guests!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.82,0:07:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, Mr. Taka. But you'd like to\Nsee what she can do, wouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.03,0:07:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we go home yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for socializing now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.77,0:07:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What a waste of time.\N- Don't complain, Revy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.20,0:07:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a way to keep things\Nmoving smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it takes care of things without\Nincident, then it's a small price to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.11,0:07:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand it.\NIt'd be faster to make them drink...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.25,0:07:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...cresol cocktails.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.65,0:07:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.59,0:07:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I hear you're a gunman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.66,0:07:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't speak no stinking Japanese.\NSpeak English.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.07,0:07:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. How's this, then?\NThis is my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.93,0:07:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't run a place like this\Nwithout speaking English.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.87,0:08:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey cutie. You from Roanapur, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.11,0:08:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rumor says that place\Nhas more bad ass motherfuckers...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.01,0:08:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...than a supermax prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Have you ever shot anyone?\NI've shot about ten guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.42,0:08:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Romeo. Can I tell you one thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your breath stinks, dimwit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.26,0:08:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can smell it over your cologne.\NYour insides are rotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.50,0:08:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy. Revy, let's go.\NMiss Balalaika is waiting. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.37,0:08:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mr. Interpreter. Can't you tell?\NWe're talking. Please don't barge in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.51,0:08:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy. Go on ahead.\NGo back and get Mr. Bando or...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Who do you think you are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.32,0:08:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you ignore me. When I snap,\NI have trouble controlling myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:08:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You listening?! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, lady. He's getting beat up\Npretty bad. Not very cool, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.54,0:09:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not give me a try? You can't be\Nsatisfied being with a weakling like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?! Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.68,0:09:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing, Chaka?!\NWhat is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not the time or place for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.39,0:09:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were just playing around.\NCome on, Mr. Yoshida.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.92,0:09:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry.\NI'll have a talk with him later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An incompetent officer and\Na soldier who ignores orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.33,0:09:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hardly stand it, Sergeant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.33,0:09:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would have been better\Nif it were a battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.60,0:09:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'd be killed off\Nin battle and discarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had his hand on his gun\Nthe whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.18,0:09:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't after me.\NHe wanted you to draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.28,0:09:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're beginning to develop a soul of\Ndiamond. You're absolutely right, Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.05,0:09:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may need my Cutlass, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.59,0:09:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hey, Revy!\N- I don't plan on starting anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:10:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But at some point,\Nthat guy will turn his gun on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.59,0:10:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is a pea brain who can't\Ntell his ass from his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.06,0:10:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's accept his challenge.\NWe'll just wait until then, Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.57,0:10:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that time comes,\NI'll kill him, for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.77,0:10:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you please pass\Nme the miso?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.51,0:10:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. We don't have enough power\Nto shut the Kousa clan up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.18,0:10:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a good plan, despite the\NPeacekeeping Council's decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought money would take care of\Nmatters instead of reasoning with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.56,0:10:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But because of those Russians...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Boss, the sweetened sake, please.\N- Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.16,0:10:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, this isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything else\Nyou need, Benny?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thanks a lot. You're a great help.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.44,0:10:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I prefer not to go through\Nthe black market in Bangkok.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh yeah, Revy wanted something.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.74,0:10:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She wants you to send\Nher Sword Cutlass.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.21,0:10:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A troubling request, I must say.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.82,0:11:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Is a storm brewing?\N- {\i1}I don't know yet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I sure hope not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.25,0:11:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- {\i1}So do I. I'll take care of it.{\i0}\N- Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.22,0:11:06.96,Top Secondary Dialog 1080P,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Due to difficulties{\i0}\N{\i1}caused by the snow...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.99,0:11:11.99,Top Secondary Dialog 1080P,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...trains in both directions{\i0}\N{\i1}aren't running.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.06,0:11:14.96,Top Secondary Dialog 1080P,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We apologize for the inconvenience.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.99,0:11:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good. I guess I'll get a cab.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.03,0:11:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You're from...\N- ...the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.59,0:11:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's been a while\Nsince I experienced the cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.06,0:11:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, with you being\Nfrom a subtropical zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.69,0:11:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you gone home yet, Mr. Okajima?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.53,0:11:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Home? Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.67,0:11:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest,\NI don't really wanna go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.60,0:11:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Okajima, you're like the old me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.77,0:11:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to hate my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I realized it's the place to return to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.08,0:11:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a family that raised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.02,0:11:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have your head on straight\Nfor someone your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.02,0:11:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My friends say I'm like an old lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.89,0:11:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no, that's not what I mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.89,0:12:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.00,0:12:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.87,0:12:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I'm just hanging in between.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.14,0:12:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel too attached to just discard it, but\NI don't have the resolution to go forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.01,0:12:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A certain Frenchman said\Nthat people are like dice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.65,0:12:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You throw yourself in the\Ndirection of your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.66,0:12:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People are free because they\Nhave the ability to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.79,0:12:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's circumstances are different,\Nbut no matter how small the choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...at the very least,\Nyou can throw yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.50,0:12:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not chance or fate.\NIt's the result of the choice you make.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.67,0:12:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.94,0:12:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can be pretty harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.61,0:12:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.68,0:12:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is Yukio.\NOh, it's you, Gin. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.05,0:12:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You worry too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.39,0:13:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'm out of the snow...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.82,0:13:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...with Mr. Okajima.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You know, the person{\i0}\N{\i1}we met at the festival.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.99,0:13:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Miss.\N- Yes? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.36,0:13:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.86,0:13:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Mr. Bando's there?\NThen I'd better hurry home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.13,0:13:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.10,0:13:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Mr. Okajima. I've gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yukio. Um...\N- Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.81,0:13:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I hadn't asked yet\Nwhat your last name is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.48,0:13:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. It's Washimine.\NSounds pretty solemn, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.00,0:13:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm against this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.07,0:13:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This has nothing to do with the Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.21,0:13:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Imagine if the Peacekeeping\NCouncil heard about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:13:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only would they not\Nallow us to rebuild our clan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.84,0:14:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...they'd kick us out of the region.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.95,0:14:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Miss!\N- You were already home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.48,0:14:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for not noticing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Bando. About what you\Nwere just talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.20,0:14:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As soon as the old man passed on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.27,0:14:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...they immediately came to us\Nabout not having a boss.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.44,0:14:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They said they'd accept\Nanyone of direct relation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Idiots, they knew very well\Nwhat that would mean.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.05,0:14:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- {\i1}Then...{\i0}\N- {\i1}That's right. A direct relation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.12,0:14:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You, Miss, are the only one.\NThose dirty bastards.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.08,0:14:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And they'll slowly come\Nto strangle us with it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.66,0:14:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yoshida?\N- {\i1}Boss! Is it you, Boss? I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.29,0:14:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a tail behind me.\NAnd it's not anyone local.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Boss!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.73,0:14:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're from higher up.\NWhen I get the chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.34,0:15:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll lose them and head to a hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.91,0:15:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Boss! The Russians aren't{\i0}\N{\i1}holding back!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.18,0:15:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They blew up a car in front of a\Npolice station when a man from Kousa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.81,0:15:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...tried to turn himself in!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.75,0:15:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.95,0:15:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What are those{\i0}\N{\i1}evil bastards thinking? I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.45,0:15:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- I hear you. I'll contact you again.\N- {\i1}Boss!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.59,0:15:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare for some trouble, and clean up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.53,0:15:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything from the Washimine clan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.56,0:15:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Nothing yet.\N- This is a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.50,0:15:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Earlier, at 0600 hours...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.80,0:15:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... a detective approached the\NWashimine office for information.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.34,0:15:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only a matter of time\Nuntil we're discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.61,0:15:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell the main unit to move\Nto the Maria Zeleska.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.44,0:15:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.\NWhat should we tell Laptev?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.91,0:15:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to tell him anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.95,0:15:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Miss Balalaika.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.55,0:15:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.62,0:15:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, um... what if the Washimine\Nclan abandons the agreement?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.46,0:15:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.03,0:15:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it concern you in any way?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.03,0:15:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.90,0:16:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Don't misinterpret\Nyour position in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.70,0:16:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sis. You're not being too nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.87,0:16:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not really a secret...\Nso why not tell him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.91,0:16:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're certainly taking his side,\NTwo-Hands. Silence is golden.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.18,0:16:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true, but Rock's on our side, right?\NTrusting each other is important, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.68,0:16:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've become a much\Nbetter talker, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.15,0:16:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, fine. Let's suppose they\Ndid something stupid like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we'd have one more name\Nto add to our target list.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.19,0:16:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our job won't change and\Nthe world will continue the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.83,0:16:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as simple as that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.43,0:16:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.23,0:16:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. We'll stay late\Nwith you to help next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.57,0:16:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Goodbye.\N- Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it easy at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.67,0:16:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Yukio, my last finals\Nwere really bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Mom made a big fuss about\Nwanting me to quit my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.72,0:16:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gin. I am involved in this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.19,0:16:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was raised in this house.{\i0}\N{\i1}I am the daughter of Ryuzo Washimine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:17:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she would keep\Nnagging me to quit my job...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.93,0:17:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}About that guy, Okajima.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.70,0:17:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He is involved in this matter.{\i0}\N{\i1}On the Russian's side.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.64,0:17:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukio! Yukio!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.94,0:17:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.\NAre you listening to me at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.17,0:17:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Oh, sorry.\N- Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.28,0:17:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a big concern for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.01,0:17:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Maki...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.25,0:17:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.72,0:17:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Never mind. On second thought,\Ndiscussing it isn't gonna help.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.22,0:17:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, don't leave me\Nhanging like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.88,0:17:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.95,0:17:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you, Yoshida.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.65,0:17:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just out for a walk.\NThere's nothing interesting about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.45,0:18:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro! You're off to meet\Nthe Russians, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.99,0:18:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time\Nsince you called me Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.99,0:18:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Bro! I'll go too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.69,0:18:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshida. Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.13,0:18:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask Gin about what to do next. You may\Nnot like him, but he's a good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.04,0:18:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.14,0:18:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.25,0:18:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.12,0:18:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- When did this happen?\N- This morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.49,0:18:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a suitcase sitting in front of\Nour office. Those god damned Russians!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshida, no matter who did it,\Nit would've ended this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.90,0:18:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had to do something about Kousa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.74,0:18:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The boss was just too smart\Nfor his own good. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.91,0:19:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What do we do now?!\N- Dark and lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.88,0:19:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The snowy night sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.89,0:19:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there! You lowlife!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.26,0:19:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.43,0:19:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to translate\Nthis in strong, blunt Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.07,0:19:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.54,0:19:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight I'll tell you about the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.54,0:19:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I seek is destruction\Nand domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.51,0:19:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any interest in\Nanything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.91,0:19:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only interested in how much\NI can dance in the pit of Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.72,0:19:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.82,0:19:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey, Rock! Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.73,0:19:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You're sweating like crazy.\N- Was I asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.86,0:19:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were breathing like\Nan old Buick engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.23,0:19:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- It's not good to drink so heavily.\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.70,0:20:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about to get wild.\NWe're moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.37,0:20:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.24,0:20:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Visotoniki are splitting\Nup into two groups...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.24,0:20:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the cargo ship and the\NRussian Embassy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.88,0:20:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is really gonna be war.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.15,0:20:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure it is. Hotel Moscow is serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A storm is coming, Rock.\NA storm of steel and blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.59,0:20:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're planning on going,\Naren't you, Gin?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.99,0:20:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I walk a path in the sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.83,0:20:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll all end up\Nwandering in darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.57,0:20:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss. You mustn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.77,0:20:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't run from this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.17,0:20:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I feel the night\Ninside of you, Gin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's body warmth.\NVery sorrowful, but therefore not cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.05,0:20:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.52,0:20:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted you to walk\Nthe path of a human...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.89,0:20:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and get hold of honest happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.49,0:20:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To this day, I have lived\Nfor that reason only.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.93,0:20:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kousa's rats and the Russian villains.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.70,0:21:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all trying to ruin us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.43,0:21:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will do what we can,\Neven if it's on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.70,0:21:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they will accept me on\Nequal terms, then it shall be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.18,0:21:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ginji.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.11,0:21:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The snowy night is beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.15,0:21:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I ever thought that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.32,0:21:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ginji.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.05,0:21:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you protect me, Ginji?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.46,0:21:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though unworthy, I am Ginji Matsuzaki,\Nlieutenant of the Washimine Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.70,0:21:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to protect you\Nwith all seven of my incarnations!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.05,0:21:47.51,Black Lagoon French,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,240)\fad(1000,0)}Man is, before all else, something which propels itself\N towards a future and is aware that it is doing so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.57,0:21:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People are just like dice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.41,0:21:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We throw ourselves into our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.52,0:23:18.52,Black Lagoon Next Episode,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10\pos(980,916)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.62,0:23:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gin. This is your first job.\NPlease work cautiously.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.55,0:23:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take care of this quickly.
